# NdArray

Object representing a multidimensional (>= 0D) array with named axes, encoded as a flat one-dimensional array in row-major order

| :--------- | :---------- | :------- | :---------- |

| data_type  | any         | ✅       |             |
| values     | List[float] | ✅       |             |
| shape      | List[float] | ❌       |             |
| axis_names | List[str]   | ❌       |             |
